<br>
With <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Vocarate Water</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, once the main tank has the foes mostly undivided attention, I stand well behind the enemy, <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> /pet back off, /pet follow me,</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> and once in position, <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> /pet attack</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  That backstab can make quite a difference.  For all pets, attacking from the rear is better, and under many circumstances I cannot sit to meditate anyway.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Razamatazz Pizzazz</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Ancient Fellowship, Xev<br>
